{"tid":1126576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梅根要請男保姆 年薪7萬鎊","createTime":"2019-04-26T13:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T15:00:47.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b7023dac0480d82e79649d465ed090378b19f1","tid":1126576,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"臨盆在即的梅根，傳媒及大眾除了關心小王子何時跟大家見面，更加關於二人在尋找保姆人選的事宜上。據知情人士透露，梅根今次他們二人經已協議好，要請一名美國籍的保姆來照顧小孩，當中梅根更偏好請到一位男性保姆。<br />\n<br />\n這名保姆更可以一反英國皇室傳統，上班時毋須要穿著制服工作，皆因梅根和哈里希望這位保姆能夠像一家人般一起生活。除了性別，另一引起英國公眾熱話的，就是這名保姆的薪酬。據說這名保姆的年薪約有70,000英鎊（約708,351港元），平均月薪約近60,000港元。現在皇室人員經已密鑼緊鼓會見候選保姆，當一輪應徵、面試結束以後，這位正式聘任的保姆將會與哈里、梅根和小寶寶一同入住溫莎的新居Frogmore Cottage。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBWiWMv.img\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBWiWMv.img&h=d3886280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3P 出梅根定哈里"},{"pid":"0c10030a12ce0aaf7d9d03c9312a63db9c04ee1b","tid":1126576,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"保<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a17cb3851a8d68ee45d476eb02c28caa5bb2af","tid":1126576,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"有錢真好"},{"pid":"42b8774c3ea38f27c3a3631d72a170a10ae92e87","tid":1126576,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"男奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a748267dedc5e139c29495d0d7b3d69d3b02142","tid":1126576,"uid":112316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"九叔與賓仔"},{"pid":"730f1c7ed8faaca591c78b21bc61f48f81563cc7","tid":1126576,"uid":38271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"rep